%description
thinkpad_acpi_events - process ThinkPad specific ACPI events
generated by thinkpad_acpi driver and log them to syslog.

You may wish to set EVENT_OTHER="thinkpad_acpi_events" in
/etc/sysconfig/powersave/events .

%prep
%setup -n %name-%version-%release

%install
